            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Does not generate content (Surfer AI credits cost extra)</li>
                <li>Pro features behind $219/mo paywall</li>
                <li>Over-optimization risk if you chase scores blindly</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Content teams that want quality control over volume.</div>
            <a href="/reviews/surfer-seo/" class="tool-cta-btn">Read review →</a>
