              <div class="per">Creator plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>WordPress, Shopify, Webflow, Wix — broader CMS than Koala</li>
