            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>More content types than Koala — ads, landing pages, social</li>
                <li>WordPress publishing + 30+ languages</li>
                <li>Built-in image generation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Credit system is confusing — cost per article hard to predict</li>
                <li>Users report charges after cancellation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Solo marketers who need broader content types than Koala.</div>
            <a href="/reviews/writesonic/" class="tool-cta-btn">Read review →</a>
          </div>
